title: Trick Knowledge ( Trick Daddy Interivew)

description:
Today on the show we had the one and only Trick Daddy stop by who spoke about his new cooking show, and gave his own knowledge on finances, STDs, Beyonce, Katt Williams, Wack 100 and so much more. Warning, we are not responsible for what may come out the rapper and radio host mouth. Moreover, Charlamagne gave "Donkey of the Day" to a Florida man that was arrested for impersonating an officer to get discount at Wendy's and Angela helped some listeners out during "Ask Yee".
